        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Starting at 15th level, when you use your Second Wind while wielding a weapon with the heavy or strength properties, if you hit with the first attack roll you make, or if one creatures fails the saving throw against your weapon&rsquo;s burst or rapid property, before the end of your next turn, you treat the hit as a critical hit. If you miss with the first attack roll you make before the end of your next turn, or one target succeeds on the saving throw against your weapon&rsquo;s burst or rapid property, you instead deal normal weapon damage.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
